            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.heading">
                <source>Configure your AI agent for Agentation</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.heading">
                <source>MCP configuration</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.intro">
                <source>Copy the block below into your coding agent's MCP config (Claude Code ~/.claude/mcp.json, Cursor settings, etc.). Annotations flow directly to your agent without copy-paste.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.label">
