            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.hint">
                <source>The snippet uses your configured API key and workspace.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.copy">
                <source>Copy to clipboard</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.mcp.noApiKey">
                <source>No API key configured. MCP only works in authenticated mode. Set Agentation.apiKey in Extension Configuration.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.heading">
                <source>How to use</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step1">
                <source>Toggle the Agentation section on in the TYPO3 Admin Panel (frontend) or in User Settings (backend).</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step2">
                <source>Browse the frontend page (or move inside the backend) and click the toolbar at the corner to annotate UI elements.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step3">
                <source>Share the annotation with your coding agent: markdown copy-paste or live MCP sync.</source>
            </trans-unit>
            <trans-unit id="module.howto.step4">
                <source>Your agent resolves selectors, file paths and computed styles directly against the codebase.</source>
            </trans-unit>
